snippet.title: A.I.L.A — TEASER TRAILER
snippet.description:
[This is not a gameplay! This is the concept of our game, so you can taste it before we launch our campaign].

A.I.L.A is the newest horror first-person game, currently in development.

In a future not so distant from our present, and in a not so distopic moment as ours, Pulsatrix Studios' newest project will unify science fiction with psychological horror in one of the hardest challenges: to find out what's your real fear, and how to trigger it. 

You'll be able to contribute with our project through our Catarse. Subscribe to our pre-campaign and stay tuned to more news: https://www.catarse.me/aila.

This project is the incredible result of our great partnerships! All thanks to @pichauinfo and @nvidiabrasil.
